候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"0814508eb062c9c19acbe0eccae0cb62ca61f491","tid":1534493,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"74a678b2cd3279419ae4e3107c7822efadc5e236","tid":1534493,"uid":195258,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"佢走得幾前丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個睇佢煮芝士榴蓮心諗做乜鳩    原來真係有人鍾意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9b7f30287514ad6a79570f7ea45bdbe2163f59","tid":1534493,"uid":65429,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"李錦聯都好成功<br />\n相信成功過唔少HKU畢業既人"},{"pid":"e3089d5b3e3cfd1bdc50f3d4617bd4eb1cdf4817","tid":1534493,"uid":152123,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦人哋依家不知幾發<br />\n真係勁嘅人 去度邊都會勁<br />\n金子到哪裡都會發光呀"},{"pid":"5558d4fac329691c17444aa128163ad6bcaa3cb8","tid":1534493,"uid":229026,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"佢唔做廚師 你就睇唔到無敵鴛鴦鏟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ce9c49057e0cf5e5782a11c11eb6737282a7d7","tid":1534493,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabe22c91936abc5ef01d4da6c3980f3f391fc73","tid":1534493,"uid":255624,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"現年51歲的李錦聯畢業於皇仁書院，90年初加入無綫婦女節目《都市閒情》做烹飪主持，打出名堂後成為師奶殺手。至95年，李錦聯表示接拍三級片，與彭丹演床戲，遭贊助商投訴後遭無綫解約。96年與艷星葉芳華拍攝電影《狂野三千響》（圖）。其後李錦聯開設調味工場及大賣「李錦雞」、乳鴿等燒味，生意不錯，至幾年前才重返無綫做烹飪主持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20110108/14846818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110108%2F14846818&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFJ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=ba26d8c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110108%2F14846818&h=ddbeef99\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20110108/14846818</a>"},{"pid":"d684b8b025a0d72de0b841e939c2166ac70ae18e","tid":1534493,"uid":72085,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:14:55.000Z","msg":"因為佢想拍住大王"},{"pid":"f1acf72ba09f28c735a4832d8499f7f2c20b9507","tid":1534493,"uid":10726,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"做廚師好失禮咩?<br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"3f8d9aff2bdd0875e3c6c622e620fadf66df1022","tid":1534493,"uid":118551,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:18:11.000Z","msg":"佢係為咗安德尊先做廚師"},{"pid":"0efee900a3168048ca33972ced1e99189ce1662f","tid":1534493,"uid":158008,"lik